data.description:
Welcome to your dream rental home! This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem is a two-story haven that combines comfort and style. Step inside to find a cozy living space with LVP and tile downstairs and plush carpeting upstairs, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. The modern kitchen is equipped with all the essentials and features a dishwasher and built in microwave for added convenience. Just off the kitchen you will find a spacious laundry room with washer and dryer included, leading into a 2 car attached garage, ensuring easy access and secure parking.Escape to the tranquility of your backyard oasis, where an above-ground pool beckons for relaxation and outdoor entertainment just outside of the screened-in lanai, making for those perfect bug-free warm summer evenings. The property also backs up to a retention pond that is blocked by wooden privacy fencing that encloses the entire backyard, but can be seen from the back bedroom windows. All four bedrooms are generously sized, located on the second floor for privacy and separation from the common areas. With three bathrooms, including a master ensuite, there's plenty of space for everyone to unwind and enjoy their own retreat. This home is not just a place to live; it's a sanctuary where comfort and convenience meet natural beauty.

What sets this home apart is its commitment to sustainability. Solar panels have been installed to harness the power of the sun, providing eco-friendly energy and significantly reducing utility costs. Embrace a more sustainable lifestyle while enjoying the comfort and beauty of this residence.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning residence your new home sweet home! Contact us today to schedule a tour and experience the charm for yourself!

*PLEASE NOTE - POOL IS DRAINED FOR WINTER
*CARPETS AND HOME SCHEDULED TO BE DEEP CLEANED
